1954;;The Black Rider;;British;;Wolf Rilla;;Jimmy Hanley, Rona Anderson;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Black_Rider_(film);;Young reporter and amateur biker Jerry Marsh investigates sightings of a hooded black figure on a motorbike. It turns out a gang of smugglers use a haunted castle as their base, deterring curious locals by pretending to be ghosts.[2]